The paper presents a set of neural networks for predicting chemical properties using multiple molecular representations. This involves the use of deep learning techniques and machine learning algorithms, which are commonly associated with the computer science sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
